welcome_message_body: "Welcome to Buenaventura Lakes, where the warm sunshine and laid-back atmosphere await you. Known for its beautiful lakes and charming neighborhoods, we invite you to explore and immerse yourself in the unique charm of our city. Enjoy your stay!"

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Orlando International Airport handles both domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: South Terminal
terminals.description: The South Terminal at Orlando International Airport is dedicated to international flights and features customs and immigration services.

wifi.note: Passengers can access free Wi-Fi throughout the airport by selecting the 'MCO Free Wi-Fi' network.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Kissimmee Gateway Airport serves all commercial and charter flights.

terminals.name: General Aviation Terminal
terminals.description: The general aviation terminal at Kissimmee Gateway Airport caters to private and corporate aircraft.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Gilbert Field Airport serves both domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Cargo Terminal
terminals.description: The cargo terminal at Gilbert Field Airport handles all freight and cargo operations.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.
